That we'd respond, Lord, in obedience.

00:56:28.560 --> 00:56:33.560
That we would take the truth of Your Word and apply it, Lord.

00:56:33.560 --> 00:56:38.640
That we'd not leave here just hearing only, but that we would leave here doing.

00:56:38.640 --> 00:56:42.280
I pray, Father, that You would work in the hearts of those that may be here that are

00:56:42.280 --> 00:56:43.480
not saved.

00:56:43.480 --> 00:56:48.840
Lord, help them to get their eyes off of everybody else and to understand their own personal

00:56:48.840 --> 00:56:52.240
situation and their need for Thee.

00:56:52.240 --> 00:56:57.400
I pray in this moment, Lord, that people would respond and that, God, You would have Your

00:56:57.400 --> 00:56:59.640
will and way in our lives.

00:56:59.640 --> 00:57:00.640
We'll thank You for it.

00:57:00.640 --> 00:57:01.640
In Christ's name we pray.

00:57:01.640 --> 00:57:01.640


